{"tid":543883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉頴匡: 請DQ新民主同盟，我無任歡迎","createTime":"2018-01-29T03:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T03:59:53.000Z","uid":134071,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"11acf99e683d88a969c16401d4c1121f5c9721b0","tid":543883,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:43:02.000Z","msg":"劉頴匡之前係新民主同盟既成員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/lauwinghong/posts/10214219329529772\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flauwinghong%2Fposts%2F10214219329529772&d=BYkiD%2BDBrvhqhOaPkH73qJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9142110e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/lauwinghong/posts/10214219329529772</a><br />\n<br />\n劉頴匡分享了他的帖子。<br />\n1月27日 14:22 &middot; <br />\n我早於去年年尾，公開表明我現時的政治立場，是不支持港獨，全心全意擁護和熱愛基本法。而事實上，在至少過去一年內，我記憶中亦沒有任何對外表述支持香港獨立的言論紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n因此，如果選管會決定DQ我，唯一的根據只可以是我超過一年前曾經提出過的言論。若是如此，<strong>根據選管會DQ眾志的邏輯，DQ一個人是要牽連整個政黨，那麻煩把我在以前支持港獨時加入過的政黨都一併DQ，我無任歡迎。</strong><br />\n<br />\n即管來吧，我從來不害怕。"},{"pid":"2f08f5316864efc862c032e7e0610d66e2322f55","tid":543883,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3111d296869cc6bf3f148db2a752d0f748d3989","tid":543883,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:52:10.000Z","msg":"攬炒咁大仇口"},{"pid":"1e057083f2e2442b108535737c65c868dfac011b","tid":543883,"uid":41602,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"啱呀！<br />\nDQ犯國威條垃圾就最好"},{"pid":"977871e79efadeab354cb0ecfa96a8cd549bab43","tid":543883,"uid":32588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:56:49.000Z","msg":"范國威已收到確認<br />\n<br />\n同政府講邏輯，講道理，根本係嘥氣"},{"pid":"a5d1699840ca50c7698798a1f153fdf74dfccfc6","tid":543883,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"977871e79efadeab354cb0ecfa96a8cd549bab43","tid":543883,"uid":32588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:56:49.000Z","msg":"范國威已收到確認<br />\n<br />\n同政府講邏輯，講道理，根本係嘥氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T03:59:53.000Z","msg":"港獨份子有咩資格同政府溝通？大家的立場根本天淵之別，唔可能共存。"}]}